# bin/ — framework scripts (T-3a0)

Invocation convention (fixed per implementation-plan Prerequisites, challenge finding #2a):
scripts are run FROM THE REPO ROOT and take a repo-root-relative path.

    bin/validate-skills.sh <repo-root-relative-path>   # e.g. bin/validate-skills.sh reporting/report-generation.md
    bin/build-skill.sh     <repo-root-relative-path>   # (Phase 3)

Never prefix paths with `coupler-io-skills/`. Paths are bare, repo-root-relative
(`_framework/...`, `analytics/...`, `marketing/...`).
Requires: bash + POSIX grep/wc/awk/sed (macOS default). No other dependencies.
